// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XX2cR1 aspect balanced rnd subdivide 3d, 2024 by jt
// 3d-version of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtdyzl aspect-balanced random subdivide
// rendered using https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lXGGR3 raymarch voxels with color

// Explore subdivision of space into cuboids.
// Subdivide by aspect to avoid too unbalanced cuboids.
// Using hybrid voxel-dda/raymarch sdf method for speedup.

// NOTE: Unfortunately NOT every tiling can be achieved by this method, e.g.
//
//       *---*-*
//       |   | |
//       *-*-* |
//       | | | |
//       | *-*-*
//       | |   |
//       *-*---*

// TODO: Method that can describe ALL possible tilings with rectangles?

// tags: 3d, binary, random, tree, plane, tiling, tile, euclidean, subdivision, tesselation, aspect, kd, balanced, dda, hybrid, raymarch, sdf

